


MAIN_LOOP  READ CURRENT STATE 
           DISPATCHER(CURRENT STATE )
           BRA MAIN_LOOP

;DISPATCHER 

DISPATCHER 



STAND BY STATE 
    WAIT FOR INITIATION BY BUMPER PUSH 


START STATE 
    INITIATE MOTOR 
    SET TIMER FOR 1 SEC OR SOMETHING 
    JSR INIT_FORWARD ( DO MOTOR STUFF )
    CONTINUE READING STATES
    JMP MAIN_LOOP



FOLLOW STATE    
    


BUMP STATE 


